Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我通过全世界媒体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想向日前要求引渡罗德·吉普利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并对我国发起攻击的PLANT最高评议会议长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔伯特·狄兰达尔先生传达讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Cosmos的盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个向PLANT发射核弹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用大规模杀伤兵器烧毁城市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把孩子当成战争机器的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么奥布不惜战斗也要袒护他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对它…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要被她的形象所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她人会在奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一样长相 一样声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:01:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一样名字的人在狄兰达尔议长身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我身为西盖尔·克莱茵之女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次大战中与Archangel并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在也和那时一样与那艘船一同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在奥布的阿斯哈代表身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她和我不同 信念也不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先要告诉大家这点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有支持狄兰达尔议长的言行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止这边的放送
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管了快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被他们牵着鼻子走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不战也没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错全在煽动战争的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡商人Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长的话是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是真相吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是自然人 也不是Coordinator
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错的是他们 世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要陷入为自己开脱的语言陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然我并不打算袒护吉普利尔氏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即联系奥布政府
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而也不相信狄兰达尔议长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须看得更清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狄兰达尔议长真正的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有两个拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在奥布…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 再派一艘穿梭机 立刻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是个事故
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止是你 我也吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底为何会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在只好稍微改变一下计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边才是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是狄兰达尔议长…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZAFT不是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏的是Logos和联合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布是他们的同伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁让我们受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是谁解放了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布是联合的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁信站在他们一边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你暂时藏身起来较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会亏待你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你世界才能真正得救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和民众也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我绝不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以只是很短一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 拉克丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们按计划去Messiah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球的联合军动向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 目前还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 世事真是难料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 虽说是冒牌货…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一头雾水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 唯一清楚的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的长官不是拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是受她的命令行事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰队司令部来电
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva归航卡潘塔利亚后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即出发与月球舰队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这 这下又突然要上天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个奥布的拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪边是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么连你也这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样迷惑我们正是敌人的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕大家都会这样在意真伪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺有深度的心理战嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么人会在意这些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为真的就都是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假的就是邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎那些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这个就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起那些 我们还有其他必须考虑的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom和阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰…是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活着待在Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶这机体的就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…梅琳也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅琳也还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但若活着 也就有可能在那艘船里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gounod距离预定地点还有20分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem发电机运转率85%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,23号至55号 临界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能量传输良好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超镜面反射器 临界偏差3129
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,预备冷却器GR启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管道连接
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 您真的要发射这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是为此才特地前来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的话真值得信赖 甚感宽心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们在这种地方勤奋工作也有所回报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近以需要为由斥巨资建造
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关键时刻又不敢发射的软弱政治家太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来我们军人到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不由得会这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是总统那种胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是狄兰达尔那种梦想家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该出手时就出手 为了保护
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啧 和报告一样为数不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是到底为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 不过肯定不是什么友好设施
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:11:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12宙域有奇怪举动?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是在防卫警戒区域外 行动有所迟缓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说有圆柱型殖民地在缓慢移动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向PLANT吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 虽然距离还有很远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前往警戒的玖尔队 贾尼斯队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前正和其护卫舰队作战中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后这个报告为最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gounod 到达指定位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,采取制动了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faure、Czerny
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姿势稳定 力场展开中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem发电机启动中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离临界点480秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 想干什么勾当
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 总之阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绕到引擎部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰塞克来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的移动殖民地有后续报告吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为目的不明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以命令玖尔队忧先考虑阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,护卫舰队从射线轴撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aprilius
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是警告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准 PLANT首都Aprilius
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,输入目标地点 Aprilius
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最终保险解除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全发电机提升至临界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一乐章 准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem系统发射准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,击发器开启 开始倒计时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离发射 T-35
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射权给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始弹奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狄兰达尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,献给你们的Requiem
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.72,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,Requiem:镇魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球背面高能量体发生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全军撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光束弯曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里来的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Januarius 1到4号直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,December 7号8号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为受到Januarius 4号撞击损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Januarius?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 Gounod的发射角偏离了计算值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是战斗的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让Aprilius逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Januarius?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有December?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从月球背面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到用这种方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打下这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有第二发的话这次PLANT真的完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都得打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Januarius 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吉普利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从月球背面发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁我们照常警戒正面Arzachel基地的空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daedalus竟然有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会是从背面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在废弃殖民地中搭载了大型能量偏向装甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分数段扭曲光束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个系统不论炮口在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据扭曲点数量和位置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能指哪打哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔的工艺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放跑吉普利尔 是我们的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么放跑吉普利尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论怎么说 我们当时必须杀死他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 出击准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家接连作战一定很累
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到关键时刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不努力就无家可归了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎最大 Minerva出击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和Genesis的时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经无可救药
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 PLANT当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事大家肯定也厌恶了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 被打后还击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后又被打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种战斗的连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在无法斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁都想幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为此只有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们参加战争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长恐怕想为这个世界展示一种全新的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长说的没有战争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们不再有纷争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人天生由遗传基因决定一切的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用遗传基因?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Destiny Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天生的遗传基因决定人们的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不称职的人淘汰、调整、管理的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淘汰 调整?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种世界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确可以使大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从自己无法预知未来的不安中解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无忧无虑的生活也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以自己能决定的命运为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盼望得到一切力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类出于这种祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于开始对遗传基因动手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们Coordinator社会的究极形态
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里恐怕不会有战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为知道战斗也是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的命运会告诉你是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道这点而生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在这种社会中扮演什么角色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命运才是王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是遗传基因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他算神官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是徒劳的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不做徒劳之举吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 才没那么容易死心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:21:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.81,0:22:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上天吧 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.56,0:22:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须阻止议长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创造未来的不是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支离破碎的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未能保护的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能允许这种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦再发生就无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悔恨化作愤怒时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次觉醒的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.11,0:23:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士Gundam Seed Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.72,0:23:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变革的序曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赌上一切出击! Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:23.13,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,握った拳の強さで砕けた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:33.73,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,願いに血を流す掌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:43.78,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,果てない翼と鎖は良く似て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:54.90,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,重さで何処にも行けずに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:04:04.20,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,亡くすばかりの幼い瞳で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:14.72,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,人は還らぬ星を想う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:24.66,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,掲げたそれぞれの火を 命と咲かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:30.43,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,運んで行くことが運命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:45.04,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,輝き刻む 誰もが優しい 刻の傷痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:23.13,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,紧握的双拳粉碎了梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:33.73,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,鲜血染红了双手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:43.78,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的双翼如同枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:54.90,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,沉重得去飞不到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:04:04.20,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡充满了幼小的眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:14.72,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,星星承载着失去的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:24.66,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,让生命 像纷纷燃起的火焰般绽放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:30.43,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,命运的转动不会停息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:45.04,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,把人们温柔的光辉 化作时间的伤痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:06.76,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,君の姿は僕に似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:16.18,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,静かに泣いてるよに胸に響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:27.62,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,何も知らないほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:31.37,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,幸せというけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:38.46,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕はきっと滿足しないはずだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:44.67,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕が選んだ今を生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:48.22,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,それだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:55.77,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,君の速さは僕に似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:59.48,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,齒止めのきかなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:03.17,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,空が怖くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:10.92,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕はいつまで頑張ればいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:20.83,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,二人ならば終わらせることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:06.76,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身影与我有几分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:16.18,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,犹如静静的哭泣在心中回响
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:27.62,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:31.37,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:38.46,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我却无法满足于此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:44.67,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,接受自己选择的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:48.22,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:55.77,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,你的速度与我有几分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:59.48,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,当一切无法停止时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:03.17,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,开始害怕天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:10.92,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我要奋斗到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:20.83,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的话就会让它结束
